  <title>Set Employee Deductions</title>

  <p>To set the deductions of an employee:</p>
  <steps>
    <item><p>Log in to the Control Panel.</p></item>
    <item><p>Click the <gui style="tab">Deductions</gui> tab.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select the period in the <gui style="input">Period</gui> spin button.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select the employee you want to set the deduction with from the list.</p></item>
    <item><p>Click the column of the category of the deduction you want to set in the row of the selected employee.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select the amount you want to deduct, then press <key>Return</key>.</p></item>
  </steps>

  <note style="important">
    <p>Deductions only affect regular reports.</p>
  </note>

